WEBVTT

00:01:29.722 --> 00:01:31.612
that no matter what,

00:01:31.636 --> 00:01:33.496
he was just like everybody else.

00:01:34.916 --> 00:01:36.871
But everyday tasks for Oliver

00:01:37.604 --> 00:01:39.676
that we all take for granted

00:01:39.700 --> 00:01:41.535
were incredibly challenging.

00:01:42.803 --> 00:01:47.693
That simple act of dressing yourself --
the very thing that I adore --

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:50.332
was a nightmare for him.

00:01:51.359 --> 00:01:54.346
His form of MD does not affect his mind.

00:01:55.083 --> 00:01:57.059
His brain is an A-plus,

00:01:57.083 --> 00:01:59.900
which means he's acutely aware
of his shortcomings.